      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">User Interface</a> * <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> * Aquarium</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Amaterske_akvarium.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a8/Amaterske_akvarium.jpg/330px-Amaterske_akvarium.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"230\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a8/Amaterske_akvarium.jpg/500px-Amaterske_akvarium.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a8/Amaterske_akvarium.jpg/960px-Amaterske_akvarium.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Amaterske_akvarium.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Aquarium with plants and tropical fish <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Aquarium</b>,<br />\na sophisticated, commercial <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> by <a href=\"/ChessOK\" title=\"ChessOK\">ChessOK</a>, developed by <a href=\"/Victor_Zakharov\" title=\"Victor Zakharov\">Victor Zakharov</a> and <a href=\"/Vladimir_Makhnychev\" title=\"Vladimir Makhnychev\">Vladimir Makhnychev</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, supporting <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> and <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> engines. Aquarium is based on the fluent design as introduced by <a href=\"/Microsoft\" title=\"Microsoft\">Microsoft</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Office_2007\">Office 2007</a>, featuring a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ribbon_%28computing%29\">ribbon</a>, which is a set of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Toolbar\">toolbars</a> placed on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tab_%28GUI%29\">tabs</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. Beside the ribbon, the main window is tiled by a navigation window with multiple <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paned_window\">panes</a> to switch modes and documents, and a bigger working area with various views on that documents, that is <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">game databases</a>, generated game lists and move variation trees as result of database queries, and a single <a href=\"/Chess_Game\" title=\"Chess Game\">chess game</a>, optional with  variation trees and <a href=\"/Game_Notation\" title=\"Game Notation\">notations</a>. In game playing or analyzing mode, the working area is dominated by a board view associated with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dock_%28computing%29\">dockable</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stacking_window_manager\">stackable</a> notation-, multiple column tree-, header-, analysis- and information windows. First released as <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aquarium\">aquarium</a> for the  <a href=\"/Category:Fish\" title=\"Category:Fish\">fish</a> dubbed <a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Rybka</a>, the Aquarium GUI is also bundled with <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Screenshot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Database\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Database</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#IDeA\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">IDeA</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2008_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2008 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Chess_GUI\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess GUI</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#IDeA_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">IDeA</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshot\">Screenshot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://chessok.com/shop/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=7_1&amp;products_id=440\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"DeepRybkaInAqurium7.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/41/DeepRybkaInAqurium7.png/640px-DeepRybkaInAqurium7.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"478\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/41/DeepRybkaInAqurium7.png/960px-DeepRybkaInAqurium7.png 1.5x, /images/4/41/DeepRybkaInAqurium7.png 2x\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Rybka\" title=\"Rybka\">Deep Rybka 4</a> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aquarium</a> by <a href=\"/ChessOK\" title=\"ChessOK\">ChessOK</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Database\">Database</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Database\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Aquarium has its own proprietary <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">database</a> format, and further supports the format of its stable mate <a href=\"/Chess_Assistant\" title=\"Chess Assistant\">Chess Assistant</a>, <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">Portable Game Notation</a> and <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">Extended Position Description</a>. It can read, query and import <a href=\"/ChessBase_(Database)\" title=\"ChessBase (Database)\">ChessBase</a> <a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessBase_(Database)Formats&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ChessBase (Database)Formats (page does not exist)\">CBH-Format</a>. Aquarium can probe endgame tablebases.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"IDeA\">IDeA</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: IDeA\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Aquarium features an <b>I</b>nteractive <b>De</b>ep <b>A</b>nalysis dubbed <b>IDeA</b>, using a permanent minimaxed analysis tree, the user can interactively explore and expand during of after analysis with various engines.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessGUI\" title=\"ChessGUI\">ChessGUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chess_King&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chess King (page does not exist)\">Chess King</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessPartner\" title=\"ChessPartner\">ChessPartner GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fritz#FritzGUI\" title=\"Fritz\">Fritz GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jose&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jose (page does not exist)\">jose</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">Protocols</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shredder\" title=\"Shredder\">Shredder GUI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2008_...\">2008 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2008 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=20531\">Rybka 3 with new GUI: are they serious?!</a> by <a href=\"/Jouni_Uski\" title=\"Jouni Uski\">Jouni Uski</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 05, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22158\">Rybka GUI (Aquarium)'s screenshots II</a> by Ulysses P., <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 05, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22834\">Aquarium and Engine Matches</a> by <a href=\"/Ted_Summers\" title=\"Ted Summers\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 07, 2008</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=32952\">Aquarium (other GUIs too?) and WB support =&gt; I am shocked</a> by <a href=\"/Miguel_A._Ballicora\" title=\"Miguel A. Ballicora\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 27, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=34728\">UCI Implementation of Aquarium is broken (FEN positions)</a> by <a href=\"/Miguel_A._Ballicora\" title=\"Miguel A. Ballicora\">Miguel A. Ballicora</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 05, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37029\">is it worth going from aquarium 3 to 4</a> by Joseph, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 10, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40673\">Houdini 2 Aquarium released</a> by <a href=\"/Robert_Houdart\" title=\"Robert Houdart\">Robert Houdart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 08, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44989\">Aquarium?</a> by Carl Langan, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 03, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=2093\">Aquarium IDEA, repetitions, and minimax over cycles</a> by  kevinfat, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, September 17, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a>, <a href=\"/Graph_History_Interaction\" title=\"Graph History Interaction\">Graph History Interaction</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=2234\">Opening Book (for Aquarium)</a> by andytl755, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, January 21, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://rybkaforum.net/cgi-bin/rybkaforum/topic_show.pl?tid=28101\">Aquarium 2014</a> by Shaun, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Rybka Forum</a>, December 09, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62321\">Changes in Aquarium 2017?</a> by Matthew Friend, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2016</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=83004&amp;p=956374#p956374\">Re: ChessAssistant is also available on runway 24</a> by Werewolf, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, Saturday Dec 23, 2023</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_GUI\">Chess GUI</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: Chess GUI\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://shop.chessok.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=7_43&amp;products_id=967\">Aquarium 2023</a> - ChessOK.com</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://shop.chessok.com/index.php?main_page=index&amp;cPath=7_56\">Houdini 6 Aquarium 2019</a> - ChessOK.com&#160;» <a href=\"/Houdini\" title=\"Houdini\">Houdini</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://aquariumchess.com/tiki/tiki-index.php\">ChessOK Aquarium Tiki</a></li>\n<li>  Aquarium 2016  by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Carl_Bicknell&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Carl Bicknell (page does not exist)\">Carl Bicknell</a>,  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/Z9-0ryeOTII?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"IDeA_2\">IDeA</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: IDeA\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://aquariumchess.com/tiki/tiki-index.php?page=IDeA\">IDeA&#160;: ChessOK Aquarium Tiki</a></li>\n<li> IDea <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video Series by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Carl_Bicknell&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Carl Bicknell (page does not exist)\">Carl Bicknell</a></li></ul>\n<ol><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/MKzCMSlvQ-I\">IDeA Video 1 Introduction</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/VkFZ1inv7Ks\">Video 2: IDeA setup</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/jBZR1P8-c9E\">Video 3: Seeding an IDeA Project Manually</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/7zuGSIN5A4I\">Video 4: Seeding an IDeA Project using a database</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/sCihn2YmWKM\">Video 5: Seeding an IDeA Project using an Engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/JALGmMkUIXE\">Video 6: Which is the best IDeA Engine?</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/bWZ4LwO0DkU\">Appendix 1: Parallel Search and IDeA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/q5Hmt-alnRE\">Appendix 2: Hyper Threading and IDeA</a></li></ol>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aquarium\">Aquarium from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aquarium_%28disambiguation%29\">Aquarium (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aquarium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aquarium\">Aquarium from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chessok.com/?page_id=27966\">Lomonosov Endgame Tablebases - History Note</a> - <a href=\"/ChessOK\" title=\"ChessOK\">ChessOK</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9003994/Final_Review_The_Lowdown_on_Office_2007\">Final Review: The Lowdown on Office 2007</a> by Richard Ericson, <a href=\"/Computerworld\" title=\"Computerworld\">Computerworld</a>, October 11, 2006</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.exceluser.com/explore/surveys/ribbon/ribbon-survey-results.htm\">Excel 2007's Ribbon Hurts Productivity, Survey Shows</a> by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.exceluser.com/contact/kyd.htm\">Charley Kyd</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.exceluser.com/index.htm\">Excel User--Reports, analyses, charts, &amp; formulas for business</a>, May, 2009</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chessok.com/\">ChessOK.com: Chess shop from the developers of Rybka 4 Aquarium</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://chessok.com/shop/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;cPath=7_1&amp;products_id=440\">ChessOK, Chess Shop from the Developers of Rybka 3 Aquarium</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"htt